# Frontend Patterns

## Component Stack

- **Radix UI** primitives via **shadcn/ui** — install with `npx shadcn@latest add <component>`.
- Components live in `src/components/ui/`. Do not fork Radix behavior unnecessarily.
- Use `cn()` utility for conditional Tailwind classes.

## Animation (Motion + spring)

Spring animations via **Motion** (`motion` package). Keep lightweight — GPU-friendly props only.

| Resource | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| [`motion-animation.mdc`](motion-animation.mdc) | Tiers, spring presets, performance rules |
| `src/components/motion/` | `FadeInView`, `StaggerChildren`, `PageEnter`, `AnimatedOutlet` |

Also documented in [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) §3 conventions.

## Responsive (mobile & web)

Mobile-first layouts are required for every page and component.

| Resource | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| [`responsive-mobile-web.mdc`](responsive-mobile-web.mdc) | Breakpoints, nav, tables, touch targets |
| [`tailwindcss-mobile-first`](../../.agents/skills/tailwindcss-mobile-first/SKILL.md) skill | Deeper Tailwind responsive patterns |

Also documented in [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) §3 conventions.

## Theme (light / dark / system)

- **Provider:** `ThemeProvider` in `main.tsx` — toggles `.dark` on `<html>`
- **Toggle:** `ThemeToggle` in Header, Admin sidebar, login page
- **Tokens:** semantic CSS variables in `index.css` (`:root` + `.dark`) — no raw hex in components
- **FOUC:** inline script in `index.html` reads `localStorage` before paint
- **Persistence:** `localStorage` key `nurul-hikmah-theme`

Use Tailwind semantic classes (`bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`) so dark mode works automatically. Brand sections (hero, footer, PMB CTA) use `--gradient-hero`, `--footer-bg`, `--hero-overlay`.

## File Structure

All forms MUST use Zod schemas in `src/schemas/`. See `zod-input-validation.mdc` for full patterns.

## API Requests

All API calls use TanStack Query in `src/hooks/`. See `react-query-api.mdc` for full patterns.

## Pagination UI

```typescript
const { data, isFetching } = useNewsList({ page, per_page: 15, ...filters });
// Render: data.data (items), data.meta (pagination), data.links
```

Show skeleton loaders during `isFetching`, not full-page spinners.

## File Structure

```
src/
  components/ui/   # shadcn/Radix primitives
  components/      # feature components
  hooks/           # TanStack Query hooks
  schemas/         # Zod schemas
  lib/api.ts       # axios/fetch client
  pages/           # route pages
```
